      • obtainStructureCollector

        public static ApplicationStructureCollector obtainStructureCollector(PluginDirector pluginDirector)
        Tries to locate a suitable implementation of ApplicationStructureCollector among currently active plugins and returns the cached one upon finding.
        Should not be called before all the plugins have been loaded.
        Parameters:
        pluginDirector - a source of plugins to load the collector on behalf of
        Returns:
        current active collector or a stub one if not found
